The '''Sector Medical Facility''' was a hospital in the city of [[Bagsho]] on [[Nim Drovis]]. It was once administered by the [[Ho'Din/Legends|Ho'Din]] [[Ism Oolos]]. In [[25 ABY/Legends|25 ABY]] [[Elan]] and [[Vergere]] were brought there after their fake defection from the [[Yuuzhan Vong]], and were interrogated by [[Saychel]] and [[Showolter]].

